{"thag7.1:0.1":"Theragatha 7.1 ","thag7.1:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","thag7.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag7.1:0.4":"Sundarasamuddattheragatha ","thag7.1:1.1":"“Alankata suvasana, ","thag7.1:1.2":"maladhari vibhusita; ","thag7.1:1.3":"Alattakakatapada, ","thag7.1:1.4":"padukaruyha vesika. ","thag7.1:2.1":"Paduka oruhitvana, ","thag7.1:2.2":"purato panjalikata; ","thag7.1:2.3":"Sa mam sanhena muduna, ","thag7.1:2.4":"mhitapubbam abhasatha. ","thag7.1:3.1":"Yuvasi tvam pabbajito, ","thag7.1:3.2":"titthahi mama sasane; ","thag7.1:3.3":"Bhunja manusake kame, ","thag7.1:3.4":"aham vittam dadami te; ","thag7.1:3.5":"Saccam te patijanami, ","thag7.1:3.6":"aggim va te haramaham. ","thag7.1:4.1":"Yada jinna bhavissama, ","thag7.1:4.2":"ubho dandaparayana; ","thag7.1:4.3":"Ubhopi pabbajissama, ","thag7.1:4.4":"ubhayattha kataggaho. ","thag7.1:5.1":"Tanca disvana yacantim, ","thag7.1:5.2":"vesikam panjalikatam; ","thag7.1:5.3":"Alankatam suvasanam, ","thag7.1:5.4":"maccupasamva odditam. ","thag7.1:6.1":"Tato me manasikaro, ","thag7.1:6.2":"… pe ","thag7.1:6.3":"… ","thag7.1:6.4":"nibbida samatitthatha. ","thag7.1:7.1":"Tato cittam vimucci me, ","thag7.1:7.2":"… pe ","thag7.1:7.3":"… ","thag7.1:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thag7.1:7.5":"… Sundarasamuddo thero …. "}